{"tid":1434275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警務處五年來被索償個案403宗結案 共賠1179萬","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:06:20.000Z","uid":60381,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"98454256210fd0682ed1c184ee8a6a1502e95e0d","tid":1434275,"uid":60381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"<code>律政司在回覆立法會議員有關預算案撥款的書面提問時，披露過去5年律政司代表不同政府部門民事索償和司法覆核案件中的成功數字，其中過去5年為警務署完成處理403宗索償案件，當中314宗均以和解方式處理，4宗敗訴，共賠償金額1179萬元。</code><br />\nsource: 20180412 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多位巴絲留意返 <br />\n其實警方行動期間對市民造成傷害/不公平對待<br />\n係可以對警務處處長提出民事索償 或者提告：<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n催淚煙飄入民居對平民造成傷害<br />\n非法/不合理拘捕<br />\n警方執法人員誤傷平民(朱經瑋案)<br />\n&hellip;等等<br />\n<br />\n咁多位和理非/冇參與示威嘅平民<br />\n請你地積極考慮向律師作諮詢<br />\n了解一下自己情況可否提告<br />\n<br />\n利申：核彈都唔割 <br />\n支持警察成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n拉哂班冚家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E8%A2%AB%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88403%E5%AE%97-%E5%85%B1%E8%B3%A01179%E8%90%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588403%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25B3%25A01179%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&d=2tiv49EdsLtkS%2FsM0tMlCO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=6c9fedd9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%2599%2595%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2584%259F%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588403%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%2585%25B1%25E8%25B3%25A01179%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&h=2ce06b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95%E4%BA%94%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E8%A2%AB%E7%B4%A2%E5%84%9F%E5%80%8B%